<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
(2.2.6) When in possessed body which has shooter slot but no quiver slot (e.g. Greater Kranken), average ammo damage for current shooter will not show up during inspecting(I) ammo. <p>
<a href="./MassimilianoMarangio">MassimilianoMarangio</a>: The code in object_out_desc() uses the line 
<pre>if (wield_slot(o_ptr) == INVEN_AMMO)
</pre>to test if the ammo can be used with the current shooter, but wield_slot() returns -1 if the body has no quiver slot. 
</p>
</div><div id="footer">


